open-omniscience (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of Open Omniscience MVP
  * Global scraping from 100+ news sources
  * Ethical scraping with robots.txt compliance
  * Duplicate detection with URL canonicalization and content hashing
  * SQLite and PostgreSQL database support
  * Advanced search with Boolean operators
  * CSV and JSON export
  * Modern web interface with visualizations
  * Audit logging for all scraping activities

